high_descs: Walk to the microwave on the sidetable.
Pick out the knife from the microwave.
Turn right to walk down the passage and reach the lemon on the left.
Cut the lemon on the right with the knife on the sink.
Put the knife on the sink.
Pick up a slice of the lemon from the sink.
Head down the passage on the left and take a right turn to reach the fridge.
Cool the slice of lemon in the fridge and take it out.
Head to the diningtable on the right.
Put the lemon on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold slice of lemon on the diningtable.

high_descs: Go to the microwave on the immediate right of the sidetable.
Remove the knife from inside the microwave.
Turn right, go all the way ahead, then turn left and left into the lemon.
Slice the lemon on the sink against the wall.
Place the knife on the sink.
Pick up a slice of lemon from the plate.
Go back to the area with the microwave and go a little ahead to the fridge.
Place the lemon in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn right and go straight ahead to the diningtable.
Place the lemon on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Slice a Lemon, cool it in a fridge, and place it on a DiningTable.

high_descs: turn around and look at the sidetable, then look at the microwave.
Open the microwave door and get the knife from there.
take the lemon with you to the sink.
Stand in front of the lemon.
Use the knife to slice the lemon on the sink.
take one slice of lemon with you.
walk to the kitchen with the sliced lemon from the fridge.
Put the lemon in the fridge, let it get cold and then remove it from the fridge.
Take the lemon with you over to the diningtable.
Put down the lemon on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Freeze the lemon and put it on the dining table.
